\s1 Abner Defects to David’s Camp  
\p
\v 6  \w As|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w war|strong="H4421"\w* \w continued|strong="H1961"\w* \w between|strong="H4421"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*, Abner \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w becoming|strong="H1961"\w* \w more|strong="H1961"\w* influential \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w*.  
