\s1 David Offers a Prayer to God  
\p
\v 18  \w King|strong="H4428"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* \w went|strong="H1732"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w*, \w sat|strong="H3427"\w* \w before|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* said, “\w Who|strong="H4310"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w what|strong="H4310"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w*, \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w should|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w brought|strong="H4428"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w this|strong="H3588"\w* \w point|strong="H5704"\w*?  
