\v 1  \w Then|strong="H6213"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* asked, “\w Is|strong="H3426"\w* \w anyone|strong="H3588"\w* \w still|strong="H5750"\w* \w left|strong="H3498"\w* \w from|strong="H5973"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w*, \w so|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w may|strong="H6213"\w* \w extend|strong="H6213"\w* \w kindness|strong="H2617"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w him|strong="H6213"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w sake|strong="H5668"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Jonathan|strong="H3083"\w*?”   
