\v 3  \w The|strong="H6213"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* asked, “\w Is|strong="H2617"\w* there \w not|strong="H6213"\w* someone \w left|strong="H5750"\w* \w from|strong="H1121"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w*’s \w family|strong="H1004"\w*, \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w I|strong="H1121"\w* \w may|strong="H4428"\w* \w extend|strong="H6213"\w* God’s \w kindness|strong="H2617"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w him|strong="H6213"\w*?” \w Ziba|strong="H6717"\w* said \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, “\w One|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Jonathan|strong="H3083"\w*’s \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w is|strong="H2617"\w* \w left|strong="H5750"\w*; both \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H6213"\w* \w feet|strong="H7272"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w crippled|strong="H5223"\w*.”  
