\v 11  Joab said, “\w If|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* Arameans \w start|strong="H2388"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w overpower|strong="H2388"\w* \w me|strong="H4480"\w*, \w you|strong="H4480"\w* \w come|strong="H1980"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w my|strong="H1961"\w* \w rescue|strong="H3467"\w*. \w If|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w Ammonites|strong="H1121"\w* \w start|strong="H2388"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w overpower|strong="H2388"\w* \w you|strong="H4480"\w*, \w I|strong="H1980"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w come|strong="H1980"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w your|strong="H4480"\w* \w rescue|strong="H3467"\w*.  
