\s1 Shimei Curses David and His Men  
\p
\v 5  \w Then|strong="H3318"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* \w reached|strong="H5704"\w* Bahurim. \w There|strong="H8033"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w* \w from|strong="H3318"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w*’s \w extended|strong="H3318"\w* \w family|strong="H4940"\w* \w named|strong="H8034"\w* \w Shimei|strong="H8096"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Gera|strong="H1617"\w* \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w*, yelling \w curses|strong="H7043"\w* \w as|strong="H5704"\w* \w he|strong="H5704"\w* approached.  
