\s1 The Advice of Ahithophel  
\p
\v 15  \w Now|strong="H3478"\w* \w when|strong="H3478"\w* Absalom \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w men|strong="H5971"\w* \w of|strong="H5971"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* arrived \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w*, Ahithophel \w was|strong="H3478"\w* \w with|strong="H3389"\w* \w him|strong="H3605"\w*.  
