\v 6  \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w Hushai|strong="H2365"\w* \w came|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* Absalom. Absalom \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H6213"\w*, “\w Here|strong="H2088"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* Ahithophel \w has|strong="H1697"\w* \w advised|strong="H1696"\w*. \w Should|strong="H6213"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w follow|strong="H6213"\w* \w his|strong="H6213"\w* \w advice|strong="H1697"\w*? If \w not|strong="H6213"\w*, \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w would|strong="H1697"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w recommend|strong="H1696"\w*?”   
