\v 28  \w Then|strong="H5375"\w* Ahimaaz \w called|strong="H7121"\w* \w out|strong="H3027"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, “Greetings!” \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w bowed|strong="H7812"\w* \w down|strong="H7812"\w* \w before|strong="H7121"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* face \w toward|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* ground \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w*, “\w May|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* \w praised|strong="H1288"\w* \w because|strong="H3027"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* defeated \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \w men|strong="H7121"\w* \w who|strong="H3068"\w* \w opposed|strong="H5375"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*!”   
\p
\v 29  \w The|strong="H7200"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* replied, “\w How|strong="H4100"\w* \w is|strong="H4100"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w young|strong="H5288"\w* \w man|strong="H5288"\w* Absalom?” Ahimaaz replied, “\w I|strong="H3045"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w great|strong="H1419"\w* deal \w of|strong="H4428"\w* confusion \w when|strong="H7200"\w* \w Joab|strong="H3097"\w* \w was|strong="H4428"\w* \w sending|strong="H7971"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*’s \w servant|strong="H5650"\w* \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w me|strong="H7971"\w*, \w your|strong="H7200"\w* \w servant|strong="H5650"\w*, \w but|strong="H3808"\w* \w I|strong="H3045"\w* don’t \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w it|strong="H3045"\w* \w was|strong="H4428"\w* \w all|strong="H7200"\w* \w about|strong="H3045"\w*.”  
